{"tid":2495532,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費蛇都屌鳩歐超聯","createTime":"2021-04-19T08:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T09:42:35.000Z","uid":42246,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c0a1369e87e6f8e6594621516658f3487363d2b3","tid":2495532,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"費爵爺罕見地高調出山，率先反對曼聯有份參與嘅歐超聯：「歐超聯係背叛左歐洲足球近70年嘅發展(is a move away)。以前我無論係地區球隊Dunfermline嘅球員定蘇格蘭Aberdeen領隊，贏European Cup Winners' Cup就好似爬珠 穆朗瑪峰咁。<br />\n.<br />\n愛華頓花費500M就係為左晉身歐聯嘅決心。全世界球迷都鍾意而家嘅歐聯。我教曼聯參與過4次歐聯決賽，佢地永遠都係我最特別嘅晚上。<br />\n.<br />\n我唔肯定曼聯係咪牽涉喺歐超聯之中，但我就肯定唔喺決策過程之中。」<br />\n.<br />\n費爵爺退休後甚少開咪，今次迅速以強烈嘅言辭同曼聯割蓆，睇黎曼聯參與歐超聯一事佢老人家都動左真火...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果然係廢老接受唔到新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac18053a92c61d86cfa021f77265adecf457e2e","tid":2495532,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c4cc23928d80ef9e11ac9d955723408e0034db","tid":2495532,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"歐超聯係背叛左歐洲足球近70年嘅發展<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完全唔知點解 新野唔算發展？"},{"pid":"b60c3d407761c0ffaa163d5154d5035bc173a8f3","tid":2495532,"uid":43870,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"條老嘢都嗰頭近啦 趁地淋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9472975779b34cc49f2dfb1018ac022a7a8bc74e","tid":2495532,"uid":373567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"我獌魔性澎湃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class